1
00:01:33,290 --> 00:01:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Spring was here at last.</font>

2
00:01:44,210 --> 00:01:45,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey, you broke it!</font>

3
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:46,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I did?</font>

4
00:01:46,830 --> 00:01:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Tired out already?</font>

5
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Me? Not even close!</font>

6
00:01:50,130 --> 00:01:51,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Keep at it!</font>

7
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Keep at it!</font>

8
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Everyone sure is going at it.</font>

9
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Keep at it!</font>

10
00:01:54,460 --> 00:01:57,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">One, two! One, two! One, two!</font>

11
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You disgrace the Demonic Kingdom
with your feebleness!</font>

12
00:02:04,830 --> 00:02:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Give me ten more laps!</font>

13
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What?!</font>

14
00:02:08,330 --> 00:02:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're sure hard at work.</font>

15
00:02:09,710 --> 00:02:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Discipline fosters nobility, after all.</font>

16
00:02:12,830 --> 00:02:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Why is everyone out exercising?</font>

17
00:02:15,250 --> 00:02:17,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">For the martial arts competition, of course.</font>

18
00:02:17,670 --> 00:02:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Even the girls from the town office
are taking part?</font>

19
00:02:20,330 --> 00:02:24,000
<font size="34"><b>Village Clerks</b></font>

20
00:02:20,710 --> 00:02:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They don't seem like fighters to me.</font>

21
00:02:24,210 --> 00:02:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Holding power in the Demonic Kingdom
requires martial prowess.</font>

22
00:02:29,130 --> 00:02:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It does?</font>

23
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey! No slacking!</font>

24
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've been found.</font>

25
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:35,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Excuse me, then.</font>

26
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:42,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's time to fight!</font>

27
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You got me...</font>

28
00:02:43,380 --> 00:02:44,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey!</font>

29
00:02:44,250 --> 00:02:45,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You gotta do it right!</font>

30
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hrngh!</font>

31
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Everyone seems excited
about the competition.</font>

32
00:02:50,380 --> 00:02:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Seven hundred and one!
Seven hundred and two!</font>

33
00:02:53,130 --> 00:02:55,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm headed home to train.</font>

34
00:02:55,210 --> 00:02:56,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What for?</font>

35
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I haven't used my full strength
since coming here,</font>

36
00:02:59,290 --> 00:03:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">so I need some practice.</font>

37
00:03:01,210 --> 00:03:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That was you out of practice?</font>

38
00:03:02,460 --> 00:03:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Far from my best.</font>

39
00:03:06,170 --> 00:03:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If she used her full strength...</font>

40
00:03:08,380 --> 00:03:10,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Blaargh!</font>

41
00:03:10,500 --> 00:03:11,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Actually!</font>

42
00:03:12,670 --> 00:03:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We need a referee for the event,</font>

43
00:03:15,170 --> 00:03:17,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and I don't know a thing
about martial arts.</font>

44
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But that sounds boring-</font>

45
00:03:18,830 --> 00:03:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The referee needs to be strong.</font>

46
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Someone who can show everyone
what true strength is!</font>

47
00:03:24,670 --> 00:03:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I guess you have a point.</font>

48
00:03:27,380 --> 00:03:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mayor!</font>

49
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm headed home to train.</font>

50
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Roooar!</font>

51
00:03:32,210 --> 00:03:33,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Baaah!</font>

52
00:03:34,210 --> 00:03:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I need two referees!</font>

53
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Two experts!</font>

54
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:42,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Only two truly skilled fighters
can be referees!</font>

55
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Good point!</font>

56
00:03:43,670 --> 00:03:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Makes sense.</font>

57
00:03:44,790 --> 00:03:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Great! Counting on you!</font>

58
00:03:46,290 --> 00:03:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But I still want to fight.</font>

59
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah, huh?</font>

60
00:03:49,210 --> 00:03:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We settled on having them as referees
with their own mock battle.</font>

61
00:03:54,790 --> 00:03:57,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Why the creepy laugh?</font>

62
00:03:57,040 --> 00:04:00,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll finally be able to punch you again, Tia.</font>

63
00:04:00,830 --> 00:04:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, Lulucy, has your fist ever
reached me even once before?</font>

64
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hasn't it?</font>

65
00:04:09,210 --> 00:04:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now that I think about it,
they did say they were rivals.</font>

66
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now that I think about it,
they did say they were rivals.</font>

67
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You just ate one.</font>

68
00:04:11,130 --> 00:04:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now that I think about it,
they did say they were rivals.</font>

69
00:04:11,130 --> 00:04:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Did I?</font>

70
00:04:12,170 --> 00:04:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Did I?</font>

71
00:04:12,790 --> 00:04:14,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There, there.</font>

72
00:04:14,420 --> 00:04:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Things sure are getting violent, huh?</font>

73
00:04:16,290 --> 00:04:18,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're not joining in?</font>

74
00:04:18,290 --> 00:04:22,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll act as healer for
anyone who gets injured.</font>

75
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I thought you'd want to blow things up.</font>

76
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I thought you'd want to blow things up.</font>

77
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Witness the greatest explosion ever!</font>

78
00:04:24,330 --> 00:04:25,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Witness the greatest explosion ever!</font>

79
00:04:25,630 --> 00:04:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Explosives aren't meant for people.</font>

80
00:04:28,380 --> 00:04:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">On that we agree...</font>

81
00:04:30,380 --> 00:04:36,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We should make an arena where all our
residents and guests can watch and enjoy.</font>

82
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:43,630
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Stage</b></font>

83
00:04:37,330 --> 00:04:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We'll have a stage and stadium seating.</font>

84
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:43,630
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Seats</b></font>

85
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:43,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's make space for shops
and restaurants too.</font>

86
00:04:40,630 --> 00:04:43,630
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Stall Space</b></font>

87
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They'll be able to watch and eat?</font>

88
00:04:46,710 --> 00:04:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How fancy.</font>

89
00:04:48,330 --> 00:04:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We'll have to think up some
good festival food.</font>

90
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Refreshing.</font>

91
00:04:55,460 --> 00:04:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Before long, the day was here.</font>

92
00:05:05,250 --> 00:05:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Look!</font>

93
00:05:06,330 --> 00:05:07,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wow!</font>

94
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you for inviting us here this day.</font>

95
00:05:10,830 --> 00:05:13,920
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}Demon Lord's Daughter</b></font>

96
00:05:10,830 --> 00:05:13,920
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Yuri</b></font>

97
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah, been a while.</font>

98
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is my father.</font>

99
00:05:18,710 --> 00:05:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The name is Galgardo.</font>

100
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Titular Demon Lord of the
Demonic Kingdom of Galgardo.</font>

101
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Demon Lord?</font>

102
00:05:25,130 --> 00:05:28,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What should I do?
I don't know their customs...</font>

103
00:05:28,210 --> 00:05:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Father, we need no excessive formalities.</font>

104
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Right, yes.</font>

105
00:05:32,630 --> 00:05:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I am Yuri's dad. Nice to meet you.</font>

106
00:05:35,580 --> 00:05:37,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you for joining us.</font>

107
00:05:37,580 --> 00:05:40,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I hope my daughters
aren't causing you trouble.</font>

108
00:05:40,380 --> 00:05:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No, of course not.</font>

109
00:05:41,790 --> 00:05:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's soft-spoken,</font>

110
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but he's important back in his kingdom
and must be pretty strong.</font>

111
00:05:48,330 --> 00:05:49,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Excuse me.</font>

112
00:05:50,130 --> 00:05:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You must be the mayor.</font>

113
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I am. And you are...?</font>

114
00:05:54,330 --> 00:05:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This here's my father.</font>

115
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And my grandfather!</font>

116
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Which means...</font>

117
00:05:59,710 --> 00:06:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're the Emperor Dragon?</font>

118
00:05:59,710 --> 00:06:01,330
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Emperor Dragon</b></font>

119
00:06:01,420 --> 00:06:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Nothing more than an honorary title.</font>

120
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You can call me Doze.</font>

121
00:06:05,420 --> 00:06:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sir Doze, then.</font>

122
00:06:06,330 --> 00:06:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sir Doze, then.</font>

123
00:06:06,330 --> 00:06:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is that truly the legendary dragon who...?</font>

124
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:08,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Simply Doze.</font>

125
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:08,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is that truly the legendary dragon who...?</font>

126
00:06:08,170 --> 00:06:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is that truly the legendary dragon who...?</font>

127
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes. Now say no more.</font>

128
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And with you?</font>

129
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:14,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, this? He's the Demon Lord.</font>

130
00:06:15,170 --> 00:06:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wait, really?</font>

131
00:06:16,380 --> 00:06:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yup. Yuri's father.</font>

132
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:22,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So you lead the Demonic Kingdom?</font>

133
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Indeed.</font>

134
00:06:23,670 --> 00:06:25,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That I do.</font>

135
00:06:26,540 --> 00:06:29,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you all for gathering with us.</font>

136
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:34,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We will now begin the Great Tree Village's
first martial arts competition.</font>

137
00:06:37,790 --> 00:06:39,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This should be good.</font>

138
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:41,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I-Indeed.</font>

139
00:06:41,580 --> 00:06:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Everyone sure is excited.</font>

140
00:06:43,250 --> 00:06:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is the largest event
we've ever held, after all.</font>

141
00:06:47,580 --> 00:06:51,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You know, this was supposed to be
seating for our guests.</font>

142
00:06:51,210 --> 00:06:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is better. Just sit with confidence.</font>

143
00:06:54,420 --> 00:06:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, uhhh, try not to get hurt
out there, everyone.</font>

144
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The crowd went wild.</font>

145
00:07:01,710 --> 00:07:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm getting nervous. Let's do our best!</font>

146
00:07:02,210 --> 00:07:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm getting nervous. Let's do our best!</font>

147
00:07:02,210 --> 00:07:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And we started with our first half
where anyone could join.</font>

148
00:07:05,130 --> 00:07:06,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The rules were simple.</font>

149
00:07:06,790 --> 00:07:09,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They'd draw lots for one-on-one battles.</font>

150
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:11,460
<font size="34"><b>Open Tournament Rules</b></font>

151
00:07:09,210 --> 00:07:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">To win, you had to either
knock your opponent out of the ring,</font>

152
00:07:12,460 --> 00:07:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">or we'd decide based on their headbands.</font>

153
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They were infused with protective magic</font>

154
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and would unravel whenever
a decisive blow was landed.</font>

155
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The first round pit the clerk Rosalind
against the beastwoman Mamu.</font>

156
00:07:26,130 --> 00:07:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ready?</font>

157
00:07:27,380 --> 00:07:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Set...</font>

158
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:29,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fight!</font>

159
00:07:38,420 --> 00:07:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wow, a real fight, right from the start.</font>

160
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:45,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I feel bad for thinking they'd just be
swinging sticks around.</font>

161
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:45,920
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Expectations</b></font>

162
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The winner is Rosalind!</font>

163
00:08:06,250 --> 00:08:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'd like to see the healer...</font>

164
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ooo, you've taken some serious damage.</font>

165
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:14,130
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Healing...</b></font>

166
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh my gosh, I'm really sorry!</font>

167
00:08:13,210 --> 00:08:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll be fine.</font>

168
00:08:14,460 --> 00:08:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Paging all combatants!</font>

169
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can handle broken limbs,
but reattaching things is harder work.</font>

170
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">so please refrain from tearing anything off!</font>

171
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What a terrifying announcement.</font>

172
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,750
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Round Two</b></font>

173
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:35,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hmph. Was that all?</font>

174
00:08:35,210 --> 00:08:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hup!</font>

175
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Donovan wins!</font>

176
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I didn't stand a chance.</font>

177
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Give it thirty more years and you'll be great.</font>

178
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's hardly enough to stop an elder dwarf.</font>

179
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They walked through the
monster-infested woods to get here.</font>

180
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">True.</font>

181
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">More of them have shown up since, too.</font>

182
00:08:55,170 --> 00:08:56,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I heard you have alcohol here.</font>

183
00:08:56,630 --> 00:08:58,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sure took your time.</font>

184
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Prepare to face Gruwald Raby Coll!</font>

185
00:09:02,540 --> 00:09:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No! Stay away!</font>

186
00:09:05,380 --> 00:09:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's it!</font>

187
00:09:06,710 --> 00:09:08,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Roaju wins!</font>

188
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I ran too far?!</font>

189
00:09:10,750 --> 00:09:12,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hiyah!</font>

190
00:09:18,380 --> 00:09:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The winner.</font>

191
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Accomplishment.</font>

192
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:23,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There were some more peaceful battles.</font>

193
00:09:26,290 --> 00:09:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The final battle of the open tournament
was between Flow and Sena.</font>

194
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Flow was using a sword and magic.</font>

195
00:09:34,790 --> 00:09:38,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But Sena was... bare handed?</font>

196
00:09:41,290 --> 00:09:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Flow! You look so cool!</font>

197
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Make us proud!</font>

198
00:09:45,580 --> 00:09:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm your biggest fan!</font>

199
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:48,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ready?</font>

200
00:09:48,170 --> 00:09:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fight!</font>

201
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Powers of the wind!</font>

202
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Get her!</font>

203
00:10:13,170 --> 00:10:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You can do it!</font>

204
00:10:13,170 --> 00:10:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whoa!</font>

205
00:10:14,290 --> 00:10:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wow.</font>

206
00:10:15,210 --> 00:10:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're much more aggressive than usual.</font>

207
00:10:20,460 --> 00:10:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Since when was Sena a grappler?</font>

208
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">F-L-O-W! You're amazing!</font>

209
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:27,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">F-L-O-W! You're amazing!</font>

210
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:27,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There! Finish her!</font>

211
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hup!</font>

212
00:10:32,670 --> 00:10:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She grabbed her back?!</font>

213
00:10:35,290 --> 00:10:36,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Uh-oh...</font>

214
00:10:36,290 --> 00:10:37,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aaah!</font>

215
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:39,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Uhhh...</font>

216
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They both fell together, so...
that's a tie!</font>

217
00:10:45,630 --> 00:10:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What an excellent fight.</font>

218
00:10:47,580 --> 00:10:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That concludes the open tournament.</font>

219
00:10:50,580 --> 00:10:51,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Congratulations.</font>

220
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your battles were more impressive
than I imagined.</font>

221
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The winners were given honorary medals.</font>

222
00:10:58,380 --> 00:11:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Please give another round of applause
for our brave combatants.</font>

223
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That was awesome!</font>

224
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Flow...</font>

225
00:11:02,710 --> 00:11:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You were so cool!</font>

226
00:11:02,710 --> 00:11:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes?</font>

227
00:11:03,710 --> 00:11:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You almost won!</font>

228
00:11:03,710 --> 00:11:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ahhh...</font>

229
00:11:04,790 --> 00:11:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But that was only the first half.</font>

230
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I wonder what the warrior
tournament will be like.</font>

231
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hang on, I don't see
the mayor's name on the list.</font>

232
00:11:16,710 --> 00:11:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shh, I'm sure it's supposed to be a secret.</font>

233
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Forgive me, I almost spoiled the surprise.</font>

234
00:11:23,380 --> 00:11:26,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm not some secret
unlockable character, okay?</font>

235
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We will now begin the warrior tournament!</font>

236
00:11:32,880 --> 00:11:35,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Things were simpler in this half.</font>

237
00:11:35,290 --> 00:11:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Winners would emerge when one party
was knocked out or gave up.</font>

238
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There were no restrictions on weapons.</font>

239
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Only those capable of fighting
under these rules were allowed in.</font>

240
00:11:44,170 --> 00:11:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They'd fight according to a tournament
bracket with the first battle between</font>

241
00:11:45,290 --> 00:11:51,920
<font size="34"><b>Warrior Tournament Round 1</b></font>

242
00:11:47,330 --> 00:11:51,920
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}Inferno Wolf</b></font>

243
00:11:47,330 --> 00:11:51,920
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Uno</b></font>

244
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Uno the inferno wolf</font>

245
00:11:49,580 --> 00:11:51,920
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}Lamia</b></font>

246
00:11:49,580 --> 00:11:51,920
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Junea</b></font>

247
00:11:49,590 --> 00:11:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and Junea the lamia.</font>

248
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can do this.</font>

249
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's one-on-one this time...</font>

250
00:11:58,420 --> 00:12:00,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She seems pained.</font>

251
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The wolves did nearly exterminate
her people, after all.</font>

252
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh yeah, that was my fault.</font>

253
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let the battle begin!</font>

254
00:12:21,290 --> 00:12:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wow!</font>

255
00:12:22,380 --> 00:12:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She's making full use of her form.</font>

256
00:12:26,880 --> 00:12:29,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is what I had long trained for.</font>

257
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Do you concede?</font>

258
00:12:42,290 --> 00:12:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well?</font>

259
00:12:43,540 --> 00:12:45,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I concede!</font>

260
00:12:46,920 --> 00:12:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Never knew they could do that.</font>

261
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Stories of a single inferno wolf
destroying entire towns might be true.</font>

262
00:12:54,420 --> 00:12:56,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Uno wins!</font>

263
00:12:57,960 --> 00:13:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The next round pitted Daga the lizardman</font>

264
00:13:03,420 --> 00:13:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">against one of Zabuton's offspring, Makura.</font>

265
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:08,750
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}Flashback</b></font>

266
00:13:07,290 --> 00:13:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You want to join?</font>

267
00:13:09,250 --> 00:13:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay, but we can't just call you
"Zabuton's offspring" then.</font>

268
00:13:13,710 --> 00:13:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You need a name...</font>

269
00:13:15,830 --> 00:13:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're rounder, so maybe "Makura,"
which means pillow?</font>

270
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, I take it you like it.</font>

271
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:22,170
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}New Name: Makura</b></font>

272
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hup!</font>

273
00:13:26,710 --> 00:13:27,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hiyah!</font>

274
00:13:28,250 --> 00:13:29,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It just keeps running.</font>

275
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:31,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Daga has the upper hand.</font>

276
00:13:31,460 --> 00:13:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Are you sure?</font>

277
00:13:37,710 --> 00:13:39,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's nowhere left to run...</font>

278
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I am defeated.</font>

279
00:13:43,500 --> 00:13:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The winner is Makura!</font>

280
00:13:46,540 --> 00:13:48,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I stood no chance...</font>

281
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Should it be that strong?</font>

282
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Good luck!</font>

283
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Go get 'em!</font>

284
00:13:53,670 --> 00:13:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Next, round three!</font>

285
00:13:55,790 --> 00:14:01,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ya the mountain elf versus
our guest from Howling Village, Garf!</font>

286
00:14:02,710 --> 00:14:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ready...</font>

287
00:14:04,710 --> 00:14:05,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fight!</font>

288
00:14:06,210 --> 00:14:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Brace yourself.</font>

289
00:14:16,380 --> 00:14:18,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This looks easy for Garf.</font>

290
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He seems pretty composed.</font>

291
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's the greatest warrior
in Howling Village!</font>

292
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:28,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Must be hard to face him
with a weapon like that.</font>

293
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It puts her at a disadvantage.</font>

294
00:14:31,170 --> 00:14:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Which leaves her only one option.</font>

295
00:14:34,460 --> 00:14:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A single strike charged with magic!</font>

296
00:14:37,250 --> 00:14:40,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hiyaaah!</font>

297
00:14:46,710 --> 00:14:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oop!</font>

298
00:14:47,630 --> 00:14:50,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whew, that was close.</font>

299
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:53,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aww, I didn't hit him at the right angle!</font>

300
00:14:53,330 --> 00:14:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ya gave up, making Garf
the winner of round three.</font>

301
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Go get 'em!</font>

302
00:14:58,080 --> 00:14:59,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Next was round four.</font>

303
00:14:59,670 --> 00:15:00,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Next...</font>

304
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:04,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Representing the high elves is Lea.</font>

305
00:15:05,170 --> 00:15:08,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Her opponent, the angel Granmaria!</font>

306
00:15:09,130 --> 00:15:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The rules will be altered this round.</font>

307
00:15:11,250 --> 00:15:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Falling from the stage
will no longer end the match.</font>

308
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That wouldn't be fair when one can fly.</font>

309
00:15:16,830 --> 00:15:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're not using your usual weapon?</font>

310
00:15:19,250 --> 00:15:20,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No...</font>

311
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I would be unable to hold back
if I used my spear.</font>

312
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:26,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm quite fine facing your full force.</font>

313
00:15:27,500 --> 00:15:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ready?</font>

314
00:15:29,040 --> 00:15:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fight!</font>

315
00:15:43,380 --> 00:15:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You do well hiding yourself. However...</font>

316
00:15:49,460 --> 00:15:51,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">from up above, all is clear...</font>

317
00:15:58,040 --> 00:15:59,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hiyah!</font>

318
00:16:07,580 --> 00:16:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well? Care to concede?</font>

319
00:16:10,830 --> 00:16:12,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Never!</font>

320
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:16,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You may have thought pinning someone
small like me would earn you the win.</font>

321
00:16:16,330 --> 00:16:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But your entire weight is not
half that of my spear!</font>

322
00:16:24,210 --> 00:16:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now you're just being rash!</font>

323
00:16:27,040 --> 00:16:28,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fine then!</font>

324
00:16:38,130 --> 00:16:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Which of us is rash now?</font>

325
00:16:42,670 --> 00:16:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All I need to do is stand and I win.</font>

326
00:16:49,330 --> 00:16:51,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But I can't...</font>

327
00:16:53,670 --> 00:16:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is that a tie?</font>

328
00:16:55,460 --> 00:16:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That was an epic battle.</font>

329
00:16:58,130 --> 00:17:03,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But the truly epic battles had not yet begun.</font>

330
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:04,130
<font size="34"><b>Warrior Tournament Round 5</b></font>

331
00:17:02,210 --> 00:17:04,130
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Tia</b></font>

332
00:17:03,210 --> 00:17:06,250
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Kudel</b></font>

333
00:17:04,210 --> 00:17:06,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't hold back now.</font>

334
00:17:06,330 --> 00:17:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes, of course not...</font>

335
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:10,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Begin...</font>

336
00:17:11,790 --> 00:17:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Tia wins!</font>

337
00:17:13,210 --> 00:17:15,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oww! No one can beat that!</font>

338
00:17:15,460 --> 00:17:17,380
<font size="34"><b>Warrior Tournament Round 6</b></font>

339
00:17:15,830 --> 00:17:19,130
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Corone</b></font>

340
00:17:16,460 --> 00:17:17,380
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Lu Lulucy</b></font>

341
00:17:17,460 --> 00:17:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Come on then.</font>

342
00:17:19,210 --> 00:17:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm done for...</font>

343
00:17:20,460 --> 00:17:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Begin...</font>

344
00:17:22,920 --> 00:17:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The winner is Lu!</font>

345
00:17:25,460 --> 00:17:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I thought I was done for.</font>

346
00:17:25,460 --> 00:17:30,130
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Fully Healed</b></font>

347
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ugh...</font>

348
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's finally time!</font>

349
00:17:30,580 --> 00:17:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I need to record my sister
in all her gallant glory!</font>

350
00:17:33,500 --> 00:17:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is it really okay for our healer
to be up here?</font>

351
00:17:36,130 --> 00:17:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Why?</font>

352
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She'll never get hurt.</font>

353
00:17:39,330 --> 00:17:40,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She won't?</font>

354
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lu!</font>

355
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shall we then?</font>

356
00:17:57,500 --> 00:17:58,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's.</font>

357
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ready...</font>

358
00:18:01,790 --> 00:18:03,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fight!</font>

359
00:18:07,330 --> 00:18:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wha?!</font>

360
00:18:09,460 --> 00:18:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What is this?</font>

361
00:18:10,830 --> 00:18:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I don't even understand
what's going on!</font>

362
00:18:13,380 --> 00:18:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lu! Lu! Lu!</font>

363
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:17,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lu! Lu! Lu!</font>

364
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:17,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is everyone else following along?</font>

365
00:18:17,210 --> 00:18:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lu! Lu! Lu!</font>

366
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lu! Lu! Lu!</font>

367
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay then...</font>

368
00:18:24,540 --> 00:18:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There they are!</font>

369
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This spear really does
boost my physical abilities.</font>

370
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My eyes can now just barely keep up.</font>

371
00:18:41,710 --> 00:18:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is incredible!</font>

372
00:18:43,170 --> 00:18:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There! Blow her up!</font>

373
00:18:44,670 --> 00:18:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Here I go!</font>

374
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:53,920
